ns0:Concept.displayName: Assessment of psychosocial issues specific to patient medication management (procedure)

ns0:DescribedValueSet.ns0:Purpose: (Clinical Focus: The intent is to capture the procedure of performing a psychosocial assessment.),(Data Element Scope: This data element maps to the QDM Intervention category.),(Inclusion Criteria: Persons with cancer during treatment or follow up care encounter should receive assessment.),(Exclusion Criteria: Persons with cancer receiving care unrelated to cancer treatment or follow up evaluation.)
